{"tid":381113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣，不停為人犧牲自己？","createTime":"2017-08-30T15:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T23:48:39.000Z","uid":68626,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25198b1efd56b25041b59ed8eb18f3d6ae96107a","tid":381113,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"天生注定係一個犧牲者<br />\n因為自己咩都唔需要<br />\n唯一需要既係感覺到人地需要自己<br />\n無物慾 無權力慾 拒絕唔到其他人向自己求救<br />\n但係永遠無人留意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ddc553fbd22b391a5ca3985f413217460bfc3b","tid":381113,"uid":72771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45d3a0c0948a5561f6cdde6a5c6f8d00931154e","tid":381113,"uid":114271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"你唔係冇慾望 你嘅慾望係藉住幫人想人認同你<br />\n所以你先會道出冇人留意你呢個事實<br />\n<br />\nBtw乜撚野天生注定犧牲者真係中二到不得了嘅諗法<br />\n全部都係選擇 唔好講咩注唔注定<br />\n做「好人」係你揀嘅"},{"pid":"f28a7e286af2a1e71d1ae803a954119204733e72","tid":381113,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔係冇慾望 你嘅慾望係藉住幫人想人認同你<br />\n所以你先會道出冇人留意你呢個事實<br />\n<br />\nBtw乜撚野天生注定犧牲者真係中二到不得了嘅諗法<br />\n全部都係選擇 唔好講咩注唔注定<br />\n做「好人」係你揀嘅</blockquote><br />\n無人注定做窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3654cdecf38c870202f8bc17195695735b7ef04b","tid":381113,"uid":129187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"唔好講到咁偉大，只不過係冇人願意為你犧牲"},{"pid":"8f3ee5d539957e5da5cc63fbadff2f991b0e2f17","tid":381113,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae49777eb8ce83be3e19cc0a3679394950045091","tid":381113,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好講到咁偉大，只不過係冇人願意為你犧牲</blockquote><br />\n有咩因果關係"},{"pid":"85b4f81545fee29df414fadd8d282db5a654c7d9","tid":381113,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"f47365e2c4f5c3eec4003d7d4b236752042358b4","tid":381113,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72435319694b0aad12e4e4700dd40c0393923d3d","tid":381113,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span></blockquote>做咩呀,屌你老母。</blockquote><br />\nOP係果個post潛水"},{"pid":"4677e7cf04316d7e49ebab8d68d31a08e20bbb3c","tid":381113,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你唔係冇慾望 你嘅慾望係藉住幫人想人認同你<br />\n所以你先會道出冇人留意你呢個事實<br />\n<br />\nBtw乜撚野天生注定犧牲者真係中二到不得了嘅諗法<br />\n全部都係選擇 唔好講咩注唔注定<br />\n做「好人」係你揀嘅</blockquote><br />\n無人注定做窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都on撚9攞做好人同窮撚黎比<br />\n做好人就算外來環境因素點影響你都可以選擇唔做<br />\n窮撚你出生於咩家庭根本冇得揀<br />\n樓主柒完未"},{"pid":"bb89dc6ce2f5beeaa826075f68a472aba6e02eff","tid":381113,"uid":141730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"唔差在做好小小啦 人地好做啲 <br />\n有時有啲野 自己唔想做就算 但諗到人地都唔想做就自己死死氣做埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無謂令件事發大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSor 1999<img src=\"/assets